text: Biden’s plan will immediately let in 25,000 asylum-seekers who’d been waiting in Mexico as their cases were judged.
During an interview broadcast on March 16, 2021, U.S. President Joe Biden said don't come to migrants considering trips to the U.S.-Mexico border to seek asylum in America.
